Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:00.30,1:24:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到什么时候 \N今年吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:03.10,1:24:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人他也OK吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:06.17,1:24:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的话比我小也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.64,1:24:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:09.51,1:24:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我大或高中生都
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:12.84,1:24:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮有趣的啊 跟高中生交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:19.25,1:24:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男校就更棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:23.92,1:24:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:26.59,1:24:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有过耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:29.66,1:24:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,70岁是爷爷了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:33.40,1:24:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的不错的话就
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:37.67,1:24:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不管年纪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:46.48,1:24:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:49.28,1:24:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都麻了\N好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:53.68,1:24:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:56.35,1:24:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:02.09,1:25:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:05.16,1:25:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都红了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:09.83,1:25:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太能喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:16.37,1:25:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:19.71,1:25:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再聊吧\N想做别的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:23.85,1:25:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N看镜头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:27.18,1:25:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要干嘛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:41.46,1:25:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好红 惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.60,1:25:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:51.74,1:25:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺着喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:57.61,1:26:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天干嘛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:17.77,1:26:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 有点重吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:43.53,1:26:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:51.53,1:26:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:03.68,1:27:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:13.96,1:27:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:16.09,1:27:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面抱住我这
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:24.23,1:27:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想这样看电影耶\N来看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:33.44,1:27:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喝醉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:40.78,1:27:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:45.59,1:27:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有舒服的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:14.42,1:28:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了 都红了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:21.36,1:28:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好红
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:46.72,1:28:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:48.72,1:28:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但会看到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:52.46,1:28:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:57.26,1:29:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:03.67,1:29:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亮亮的好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:07.00,1:29:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着可爱的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:09.67,1:29:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:59.06,1:30:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:13.20,1:30:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:28.82,1:30:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉高好玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:34.82,1:30:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:38.16,1:30:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:38.43,1:30:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:41.36,1:30:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:49.64,1:30:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:19.60,1:32:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:52.83,1:32:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好红喔 好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:33.54,1:33:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:25.46,1:34:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:27.72,1:34:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直舔嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:57.49,1:35:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:07.76,1:35:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:30.19,1:35:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了耶 抱歉我变这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:49.14,1:35:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿嗒嗒的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:19.17,1:36:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也 想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:39.59,1:36:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:24.42,1:39:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来好吗 受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:32.62,1:40:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:36.42,1:41:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:40.02,1:41:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:57.11,1:42:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:14.19,1:42:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:17.26,1:42:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:24.33,1:42:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:46.76,1:42:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:59.44,1:43:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:01.57,1:43:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢从后面吗\N其实想看脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:46.82,1:43:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓我屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:58.03,1:44:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:22.19,1:44:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:37.80,1:44:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:56.22,1:44:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:01.62,1:46:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看？\N想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:03.75,1:46:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:09.49,1:46:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:14.43,1:46:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:22.84,1:46:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:28.18,1:46:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:44.59,1:46:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:05.01,1:47:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:11.15,1:47:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:15.69,1:47:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射吗\N在忍耐着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:40.25,1:47:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了？不用忍耐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:49.73,1:47:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:09.35,1:48:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:16.15,1:48:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有吗\N还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:38.98,1:48:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变敏感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:51.25,1:48:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:54.46,1:48:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:00.06,1:49:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我也爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:04.60,1:49:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗 好多汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:15.41,1:49:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:22.09,1:49:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵着耶 \N对 牵着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:24.62,1:49:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沾到了有面纸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:26.62,1:49:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:35.83,1:49:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:38.50,1:49:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:40.90,1:49:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再去拿喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:51.45,1:49:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:53.32,1:49:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此 好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:01.72,1:50:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 \N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:05.60,1:50:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有拍好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:06.66,1:50:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太兴奋 不记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:09.33,1:50:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:12.54,1:50:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝醉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:16.01,1:50:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看都红了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:21.34,1:50:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好红喔 红吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:25.08,1:50:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就在喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:30.02,1:50:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了\N谢谢搞我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:35.23,1:50:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了吧\N100分
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:43.50,1:50:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:45.90,1:50:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要YA
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:48.30,1:50:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该回去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:52.71,1:50:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想洗澡\N洗澡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:56.18,1:51:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗好再走\N要回去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:01.25,1:51:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:03.79,1:51:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:13.93,1:51:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但得到300分了不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:18.74,1:51:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴都精液吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:20.60,1:51:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:25.14,1:51:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备一下回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:30.88,1:51:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯\N干怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:37.69,1:51:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢招待\N彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:40.62,1:51:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢搞我喔\N再找我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:46.36,1:51:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再听我的烦恼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:49.70,1:51:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢搞我 好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:56.11,1:51:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以回想喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:58.64,1:52:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:01.71,1:52:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大既会吧\N真的吗 今天也
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:08.52,1:52:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢搞我 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:12.92,1:52:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了 抱歉 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:22.00,1:52:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:25.47,1:52:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的\N但喝了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:31.34,1:52:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:34.01,1:52:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一回结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:36.68,1:52:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二回不要喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:40.02,1:52:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 我会调整好再加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:45.36,1:52:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天先回去睡觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:49.36,1:52:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:53.10,1:52:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想喝耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:57.37,1:52:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:59.10,1:53:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小时而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:03.91,1:53:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:05.38,1:53:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住公司吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:08.44,1:53:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上叫我起床\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:14.45,1:53:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:18.72,1:53:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:23.53,1:53:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一觉到天亮 摄影第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:29.53,1:53:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我是希志
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:33.80,1:53:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:34.74,1:53:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天开始了\N开始了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:41.68,1:53:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:43.41,1:53:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没宿醉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:46.35,1:53:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少 有点怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:49.95,1:53:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天会加油\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:51.55,1:53:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不喝\N今天不能喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:57.03,1:53:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果要一起喝再喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:59.83,1:54:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啊 喝到早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:04.10,1:54:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到该去的地方吧\N走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:10.37,1:54:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得是怎样的人\N怎样的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:13.71,1:54:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年龄或外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:18.11,1:54:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这街道的气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:20.38,1:54:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的欧吉桑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:23.85,1:54:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是很大的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:27.06,1:54:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:31.06,1:54:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西洋风的耶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:33.86,1:54:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做什么
