Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:50.85,2:08:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想舔手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:58.86,2:09:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:05.54,2:09:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指就好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:32.90,2:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:50.11,2:09:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:56.12,2:09:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:05.20,2:10:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:08.80,2:10:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:22.15,2:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:28.42,2:10:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:35.23,2:10:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N让我爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:44.70,2:10:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 全部?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:50.44,2:10:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:00.98,2:11:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:05.12,2:11:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我爽\N想爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:10.33,2:11:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼罩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:14.20,2:11:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩擦好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:19.40,2:11:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔奶头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:26.08,2:11:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说不知道喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:32.62,2:11:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢 喜欢乳头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:47.70,2:11:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:55.31,2:12:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通啊 不是想爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:04.91,2:12:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再舔比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:10.12,2:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腿\N大腿 奶头好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:18.13,2:12:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:24.40,2:12:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腿吗 喜欢大腿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:31.47,2:12:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头也喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:39.22,2:12:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头也喜欢？\N要我舔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:46.16,2:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:12:47.76,2:12:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说的话 不舔唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:16.72,2:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:23.66,2:13:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:29.67,2:13:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勃起了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:34.47,2:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再摸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:39.01,2:13:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:43.15,2:13:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:46.48,2:13:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拜托啊\N请摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:55.69,2:13:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:02.23,2:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这？不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:06.64,2:14:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:10.77,2:14:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:15.04,2:14:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:22.79,2:14:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要？\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:27.19,2:14:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么样 这里想怎样\N摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:35.47,2:14:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被摸吗 怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:42.14,2:14:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:46.41,2:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来 怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:50.68,2:14:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:04.16,2:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用舌头\N奶头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:12.84,2:15:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔奶头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:18.17,2:15:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:23.78,2:15:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒\N舔肉棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:52.08,2:15:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:57.41,2:15:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:03.02,2:16:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不够吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:05.69,2:16:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:09.96,2:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:15.57,2:16:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:26.91,2:16:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:30.91,2:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢啊 早说啊\N唧唧歪歪苦么一堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:53.60,2:16:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢这吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:04.81,2:17:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想舔害羞的地方吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:21.90,2:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚抬高
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:27.24,2:17:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞\N害羞？都看到了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:39.52,2:17:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都看到了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:48.86,2:17:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒硬梆梆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:52.73,2:17:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:56.33,2:17:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:59.40,2:18:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:02.34,2:18:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也收缩着
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:12.62,2:18:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面怎么办 舔好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:22.49,2:18:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:03.60,2:19:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:21.48,2:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想干我BB吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:26.82,2:19:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以放下唷 想干我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:30.29,2:19:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:33.36,2:19:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那忍得住就好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:22.75,2:20:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐一下 还有10秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:27.15,2:20:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8 7 6 5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:37.56,2:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:03.99,2:21:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:09.46,2:21:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:12.80,2:21:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能摸喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:50.30,2:21:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:59.38,2:22:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:02.71,2:22:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这？再来？前端？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:08.05,2:22:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗 爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:31.14,2:22:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 流汁了唷 忍耐的关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:58.50,2:23:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍30秒的话 就让你干我
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:10.11,2:23:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:27.06,2:23:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4 5 6 7
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:36.67,2:23:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8 9 10 11 12 13
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:45.62,2:23:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,14 15 16 17
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:53.76,2:24:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18 19 20 21 22 23
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:03.63,2:24:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24 25 26 27 28
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:12.84,2:24:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,29 不行 要30秒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:19.65,2:24:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,27 28 29 30 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:24:43.81,2:24:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点说
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:16.64,2:25:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30秒刚好射耶\N再一次吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:27.58,2:25:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:33.46,2:25:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N说很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:42.67,2:25:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:45.47,2:25:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:49.07,2:25:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟刚刚感觉不一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:55.21,2:26:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都弄脏了擦掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:03.22,2:26:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  面纸在哪 打开好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:16.97,2:26:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:24.57,2:26:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己擦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:29.65,2:26:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:34.45,2:26:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:36.85,2:26:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 沾到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:43.53,2:26:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:46.20,2:26:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:52.20,2:26:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:26:56.61,2:27:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不管 喜欢这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:11.02,2:27:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 慢慢的\N还有下一场要干我
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:15.02,2:27:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报歉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:18.36,2:27:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 叫朋友救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:23.43,2:27:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:24.50,2:27:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:26.77,2:27:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:29.57,2:27:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:34.64,2:27:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是很努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:39.58,2:27:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没辄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:42.92,2:27:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里最努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:48.79,2:27:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中途突然变老实了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:53.20,2:27:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 很自由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:56.93,2:28:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽就说爽好吧\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:01.07,2:28:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想射了 快结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:07.34,2:28:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没被干但有被干的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:11.88,2:28:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了有爽就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:14.28,2:28:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射就是爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:18.56,2:28:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下一个地方 被干好吧\N洗澡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:23.63,2:28:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去帮可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:26.56,2:28:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:30.97,2:28:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:36.84,2:28:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的第二间\N太黑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:43.11,2:28:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:47.52,2:28:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某事务所的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:54.32,2:28:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着个
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:28:57.66,2:29:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:02.60,2:29:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的希志\N初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:07.54,2:29:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是中西安太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:12.34,2:29:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大学时就知道你希志
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:16.21,2:29:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后天天想着你希志
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:19.82,2:29:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时想到会讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:24.35,2:29:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想见到其他人 所以没参加活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:34.90,2:29:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没看过我 可能不知道我
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:40.24,2:29:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但喜欢希志不会输给任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:44.37,2:29:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话可以见面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:49.98,2:29:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想两人好好聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:52.12,2:29:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你读 等你回信\N安太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:57.59,2:30:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有回信信纸\N代你回信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:01.59,2:30:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代我？什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:06.53,2:30:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到信时决定拍摄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:13.34,2:30:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:17.34,2:30:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点重\N好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:23.35,2:30:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很重
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:27.88,2:30:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:31.35,2:30:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你用泡泡浴服务他
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:44.83,2:30:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什要泡泡浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:50.57,2:30:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就给他世界最高级的泡泡浴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:54.18,2:30:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:30:56.71,2:31:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得都这么说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:02.19,2:31:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回应他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:05.52,2:31:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这样也行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:09.39,2:31:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信上写说想聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:12.73,2:31:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做太超过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:15.40,2:31:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他说想要泡泡浴服务
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:18.74,2:31:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要带去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:21.94,2:31:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生里没拿过这么重的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:28.08,2:31:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像圣诞老人一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:39.56,2:31:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里\N上？下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:45.30,2:31:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:52.24,2:31:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:56.24,2:31:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N在家搞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:31:59.98,2:32:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家搞世界最高级泡泡浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:03.05,2:32:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧？\N不要紧吧 但都说了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:09.45,2:32:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:17.19,2:32:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:20.80,2:32:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我是希志 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:24.93,2:32:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希志啊 请进吧\N好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:28.67,2:32:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:30.27,2:32:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 东西太多了\N工作人员也可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:36.14,2:32:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以\N打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:38.95,2:32:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗 帮你拿\N不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:46.16,2:32:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重喔\N重吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:49.36,2:32:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不要的话 就说喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:32:54.83,2:33:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的啊 惨了 吓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:03.91,2:33:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧 \N好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:05.11,2:33:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法回头\N还有一人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:11.92,2:33:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了 失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:17.12,2:33:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道该看哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:24.99,2:33:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等再看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:28.87,2:33:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问名字好吗\N中西安太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:33.54,2:33:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么称呼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:36.21,2:33:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友都叫我安全的安太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:45.15,2:33:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郎拿掉叫我安太\N安太
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:52.62,2:33:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是希志 小爱 都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:59.96,2:34:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:04.50,2:34:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆 叫你小爱好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:09.31,2:34:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:13.44,2:34:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安太 有点怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:18.92,2:34:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友都叫我安太\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:25.19,2:34:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小安如何 安太好吗\N安太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:32.13,2:34:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了叫安太
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:39.47,2:34:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:44.81,2:34:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太喜欢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:48.95,2:34:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常就这状态吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:51.35,2:34:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被希志围绕生活\N所以贴成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:56.42,2:35:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才贴一半\N一半吗 好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:02.96,2:35:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想全贴的\N好棒 最近的都有耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:16.44,2:35:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔 自己做的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:19.64,2:35:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友给的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:22.71,2:35:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢最大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:27.12,2:35:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天回来都亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:32.32,2:35:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系不用了\N都说我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:40.86,2:35:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗\N看到了没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:45.27,2:35:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:48.07,2:35:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很在意的\N这什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:53.94,2:35:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱枕？\N不
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:57.28,2:35:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:58.75,2:36:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的受不了时
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:05.82,2:36:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个每晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:16.37,2:36:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:20.50,2:36:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:23.97,2:36:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看错\N这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:29.31,2:36:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看错吧\N这
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:36.25,2:36:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希志来之前受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:43.73,2:36:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射的好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:50.93,2:36:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:53.87,2:36:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DVD也 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:36:55.74,2:37:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止DVD CD也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:01.88,2:37:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了很多好歌\N抱歉是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:12.42,2:37:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是努力得到的\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:21.10,2:37:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:30.71,2:37:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:33.64,2:37:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害羞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:37.65,2:37:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我是租借妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:42.85,2:37:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想要我做的\N我什么都做
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:51.79,2:37:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有给我信
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:56.07,2:37:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天行李是泡泡浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:37:59.27,2:38:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都带来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:38:03.67,2:38:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:38:05.54,2:38:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:38:09.41,2:38:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我服务
