Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:42.39,2:56:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:30.17,2:57:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:38.58,2:57:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:45.66,2:57:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 可以干我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:52.06,2:57:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会全力加油被干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:04.61,2:58:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用湿湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:09.95,2:58:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以干我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:25.30,2:58:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:27.70,2:58:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:37.84,2:58:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入了\N全插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:50.39,2:58:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:56.39,2:59:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢动喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:59:09.07,2:59:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:59:15.35,2:59:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夸我吗\N是 在夸你 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:00:06.33,3:00:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟抱枕哪个好
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:00:10.47,3:00:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干本人爽一百倍\N太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:00:27.15,3:00:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到插入的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:00:33.96,3:00:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头也硬硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:00:57.85,3:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得到吗\N看好清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:01:23.47,3:01:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:01:43.89,3:01:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了 去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:01:51.10,3:01:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了 去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:02:04.31,3:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:02:07.92,3:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:02:16.99,3:02:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:02:43.29,3:02:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:02:47.56,3:02:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:03:02.51,3:03:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱的淫屁股好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:03:28.40,3:03:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:03:38.01,3:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行 等等 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:03:46.28,3:03:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:04:08.71,3:04:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:04:33.00,3:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:04:40.47,3:04:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:04:42.61,3:04:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:04:57.82,3:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过来动好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:05:15.57,3:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:05:51.74,3:05:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来动好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:06:21.10,3:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽\N看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:06:28.18,3:06:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:06:36.99,3:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:06:39.79,3:06:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:07:10.62,3:07:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:07:14.09,3:07:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 去了\N好喔 爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:07:25.84,3:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:07:32.51,3:07:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:07:48.39,3:07:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:08:28.70,3:08:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:08:32.57,3:08:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了\N要射了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:08:35.24,3:08:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射好吗\N好啊 射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:08:42.98,3:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:09:12.61,3:09:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:09:19.95,3:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔干净好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:06.00,3:10:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:10.93,3:10:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希志如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:17.07,3:10:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人的希志太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:20.68,3:10:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:24.68,3:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:27.75,3:10:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:32.69,3:10:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吧 谢谢你干我
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:37.09,3:10:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说真高兴 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:41.90,3:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没射我脸上没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:46.17,3:10:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 这么漂亮的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:48.97,3:10:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:52.04,3:10:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受你照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:54.04,3:10:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:10:58.18,3:11:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒 身心都疗愈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:01.25,3:11:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次活动可以的话来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:08.73,3:11:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次拿出勇气去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:12.86,3:11:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信也带来
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:14.73,3:11:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话再叫我\N我会过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:18.20,3:11:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这房间好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:21.27,3:11:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢干我
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:25.14,3:11:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握少好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:27.94,3:11:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:30.61,3:11:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力被人干吧\N我会加油被干 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:35.02,3:11:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖歉 请休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:41.29,3:11:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:50.77,3:11:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始有点想回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:57.71,3:11:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N实话
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:11:59.18,3:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实话 但 很单纯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:06.25,3:12:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以放心多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:12.12,3:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒 被干得很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:17.33,3:12:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有下一场 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:21.87,3:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:25.47,3:12:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:28.27,3:12:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 有重要的事忘了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:34.54,3:12:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影结束了\N辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:37.35,3:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这？\N辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:40.02,3:12:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还有时间嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:44.95,3:12:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:45.76,3:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可以到早上喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:48.56,3:12:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行\N什么不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:52.56,3:12:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有吧 该去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:12:57.23,3:13:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了\N骗人吧·
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:01.64,3:13:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规则是到12点
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:06.04,3:13:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧\N不是骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:10.45,3:13:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N真的想到很晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:15.12,3:13:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好啊 可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:19.66,3:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最后一班车
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:24.59,3:13:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人花太多时间\N哭么哭爸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:27.66,3:13:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家很
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:30.47,3:13:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个性太强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:35.00,3:13:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会想玩弄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:39.81,3:13:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之剩下时间只有这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:50.09,3:13:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30分？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:13:53.42,3:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30分内结束的话可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:02.63,3:14:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极限了\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:09.17,3:14:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:11.71,3:14:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想看30分
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:17.18,3:14:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间想了\N怎么办哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:18.11,3:14:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:20.38,3:14:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始\N现在开始？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:24.52,3:14:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:28.79,3:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30分吧 到要5分钟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:33.20,3:14:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:36.27,3:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:39.20,3:14:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:50.81,3:14:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我是\N希志 我来给你干了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:14:57.49,3:15:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:02.16,3:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:02.83,3:15:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:13.10,3:15:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这好讨厌 好紧张喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:15.64,3:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么准吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:34.32,3:15:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出来了 别闹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:36.46,3:15:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:42.07,3:15:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面\N初次见面 希志
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:44.60,3:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:49.27,3:15:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作人员可以吗\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:52.61,3:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:15:58.08,3:16:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫希志
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:00.88,3:16:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣是跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:03.95,3:16:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特技是 跳舞和
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:08.63,3:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的食物是拉面和辣的\N我也喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:15.57,3:16:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可以随意干我\N想怎么搞我
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:20.77,3:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理\N料理？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:26.64,3:16:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 只会做牛肉饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:30.38,3:16:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:31.98,3:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:34.65,3:16:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近吃太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:37.72,3:16:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很拿手 没自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:41.32,3:16:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的呢\N最近沉迷游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:46.26,3:16:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:47.86,3:16:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏会很兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:50.67,3:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:54.54,3:16:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被禁止耶\N禁止 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:16:57.74,3:17:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很沉迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:01.34,3:17:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打到晚上 那陪我到早上也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:04.55,3:17:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:08.02,3:17:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会超级喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:12.02,3:17:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:15.49,3:17:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:18.43,3:17:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会 这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:23.37,3:17:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难喔\N有其他的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:25.37,3:17:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有很多书\N是啊 书
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:29.24,3:17:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢国外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:32.18,3:17:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶\N都看意大利法国欧洲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:42.99,3:17:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒耶 意大利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:48.73,3:17:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 别管意大利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:52.20,3:17:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没其他的吗 有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:17:58.20,3:18:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳舞\N不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:01.14,3:18:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:04.47,3:18:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀很酸痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:07.81,3:18:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 转过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:11.41,3:18:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子 可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:13.68,3:18:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:16.09,3:18:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:22.89,3:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:44.51,3:18:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:47.72,3:18:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:51.72,3:18:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体轻松了\N是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:18:58.80,3:19:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:02.00,3:19:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:10.01,3:19:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 处理\N知道吗 最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:17.88,3:19:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:19.62,3:19:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 这如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:24.29,3:19:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:26.02,3:19:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以忍一下再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:29.76,3:19:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:36.57,3:19:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没其他想做的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:40.97,3:19:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:43.37,3:19:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想搞是想搞
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:49.11,3:19:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:19:51.92,3:19:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的比较好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:20:08.06,3:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:20:15.41,3:20:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:20:23.95,3:20:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛肉饭比较好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:20:36.76,3:20:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的可以吗 突然可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:20:43.70,3:20:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然难受了\N想被干死
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:20:47.97,3:20:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我想慢慢地被干
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:21:12.00,3:21:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这样了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:21:48.57,3:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:21:58.04,3:22:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以舔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:22:29.01,3:22:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启一
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:22:34.48,3:22:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要舔启一的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:23:17.32,3:23:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:24:50.35,3:24:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:24:53.42,3:24:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:25:09.70,3:25:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿嗒嗒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:25:29.72,3:25:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都湿了唷 爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:25:36.13,3:25:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吹的爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:26:03.09,3:26:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想射我哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:26:09.63,3:26:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我脸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:26:12.43,3:26:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:26:42.19,3:26:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是M吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:26:44.99,3:26:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢奶头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:26:53.94,3:26:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:00.48,3:27:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡？没关系 好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:06.08,3:27:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:08.62,3:27:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:11.82,3:27:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你发射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:17.03,3:27:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:21.56,3:27:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:28.24,3:27:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前端？
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:46.79,3:27:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:27:56.27,3:28:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:00.14,3:28:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:09.61,3:28:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:12.95,3:28:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到了但好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:29.77,3:28:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:32.97,3:28:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:39.38,3:28:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:43.25,3:28:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒\N就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:44.85,3:28:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒都籽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:50.72,3:28:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常没这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:28:58.06,3:29:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢射我脸上 好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:04.47,3:29:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:06.60,3:29:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:16.08,3:29:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:19.42,3:29:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:22.62,3:29:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:28.49,3:29:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 都是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:34.76,3:29:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:37.97,3:29:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽快多了 谢谢你射我
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:43.84,3:29:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:51.31,3:29:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都可以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:55.32,3:29:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点突然\N哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:29:58.39,3:30:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧 我也忍一下再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:03.59,3:30:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:06.93,3:30:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:09.33,3:30:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次带我去兜风
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:11.73,3:30:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定\N请多指教 真的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:22.41,3:30:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:25.75,3:30:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 明天要工作吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:35.09,3:30:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以洗澡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:37.49,3:30:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊借我洗澡\N请
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:41.10,3:30:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪边
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:30:43.63,3:30:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:31:57.17,3:31:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:02.11,3:32:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:07.98,3:32:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿湿的没关系吗\N没关系今天很热
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:14.12,3:32:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你射我\N下次再拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:19.20,3:32:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天工作加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:27.07,3:32:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:32.54,3:32:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:40.02,3:32:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好急喔 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:42.95,3:32:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿嗒嗒的这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:48.96,3:32:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干了耶\N好危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:52.96,3:32:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的30分就回去耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:32:57.10,3:33:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直这样就好了耶\N不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:01.50,3:33:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服弄干拍个结尾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:08.98,3:33:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房间有吹风机去借一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:11.78,3:33:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时间有啊\N有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:16.72,3:33:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想看很焦急的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:20.59,3:33:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:22.73,3:33:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那刚刚还可以搞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:26.20,3:33:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看这个\N在床上被搞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:30.07,3:33:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊\N去借吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:38.34,3:33:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 再去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:41.14,3:33:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚说再见了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:44.35,3:33:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借吹风机
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:33:47.28,3:33:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,3:34:01.16,3:34:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完
